The array of JSON Patch Objects to add the new rule would be:

```
[
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/project/rules/-",
    "value": "Pills accidentally marked as taken can be undone."
  }
]
```

Yes, you are correct. The correct path for the markAsTakenRules is indeed "project/markAsTakenRules". Thank you for pointing that out! Here's the array of patches for adding the new rule:

```
[
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/project/markAsTakenRules/-",
    "value": "Accidentally marked pills can be undone"
  }
]
```
